text: Genah Fabian (born September 5, 1989) is a New Zealand kickboxer and mixed martial artist, she is of Samoan, German descent on her mothers side, and Maori Tainui from her fathers side. ==Early career== As a youth Genah Fabian was involved in track and field events and took up Kickboxing in her early 20's after relocating to Thailand.
